00:20:37,370 --> 00:20:41,170
However, from early this morning, many people from the pugilist world have come about this again.

249
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,900
Master Shi started something again?

250
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:47,990
Yes. He announced that the auction failed last time,

251
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:50,860
thus allowing Fengming Mountain Manor to freely gain the Longevity fruit.

252
00:20:50,860 --> 00:20:52,830
He doesn't want to be involved in these matters.

253
00:20:52,830 --> 00:20:55,200
He asked for Fengming Mountain Manor to burn the fruit in front of everyone,

254
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:57,740
to halt the thoughts of greed.

255
00:20:59,210 --> 00:21:03,470
This explanation sounds very glorified but there is more.

256
00:21:03,470 --> 00:21:06,500
He suggested that in order to uphold principles of goodwill,

257
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:09,580
the people should be open to confessing their crimes.

258
00:21:10,850 --> 00:21:12,940
This Master Shi,

259
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:16,940
his schemes really are endless.

260
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:20,040
The promise of the Book of One's Crimes, those who confess

261
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:22,100
will get the Longevity fruit.

262
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:26,500
He hopes that someone will repent and absolve their sins in order to set a good example.

263
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:30,960
Supporting that path will open up to sinners who repent.

264
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:35,370
Why do I feel that he does not have such good intentions?

265
00:21:35,930 --> 00:21:39,250
Yes, for sure he doesn't have these good intentions.

266
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:43,860
He mentioned on multiple occasions that the Longevity fruit is in the hands of Miss Chun Hua.

267
00:21:43,860 --> 00:21:47,830
If we don't burn the fruit, then doubt will persist.

268
00:21:49,100 --> 00:21:52,720
Also, he mentions that Fengming Mountain Manor follows through with their promises.

269
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:54,940
A place of leadership dating back to 100 years.

270
00:21:54,940 --> 00:22:00,180
Fengming Mountain Manor is the best choice for this kind of procedural justice.

271
00:22:00,180 --> 00:22:02,150
Burning the fruit in front of the public.

272
00:22:02,150 --> 00:22:05,080
There was already much bloodshed at the auction.

273
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:09,910
Now, doubt is spreading to more people.

274
00:22:10,780 --> 00:22:13,400
I don't want to cause more trouble.

275
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:16,870
How about... I go to clear up this misunderstanding?

276
00:22:16,870 --> 00:22:21,650
No, the idea of the Book of One's Crimes is not bad.

277
00:22:21,650 --> 00:22:24,990
I hope that those big demons do come out

278
00:22:24,990 --> 00:22:26,940
and repent for their sins.

279
00:22:26,940 --> 00:22:30,760
They can get the Longevity fruit and follow the path of goodness once and for all.

280
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:35,340
But who would be the best person for this role?

281
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:46,890
Burn the Longevity fruit!

282
00:22:46,890 --> 00:22:49,710
Such a bewitching item should have been burned long ago.

283
00:22:49,710 --> 00:22:51,510
Book of One's Crimes.

284
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:55,780
In the pugilist world, there are two big demons.

285
00:22:55,780 --> 00:22:59,620
Shangguang Qiu Yue of Qianyue Sect and Fu Lou of Chuanqi Sect.

286
00:22:59,620 --> 00:23:03,270
If Fu Lou can really repent for his crimes,

287
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:06,510
then it can also settle things regarding my father's death.

288
00:23:07,020 --> 00:23:09,250
But once he admits it,

289
00:23:09,780 --> 00:23:12,450
wouldn't my father have died for nothing?

290
00:23:16,290 --> 00:23:20,560
The righteousness of the pugilist world, compared with personal grievances,

291
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:23,820
I will choose righteousness, of course.

292
00:23:23,820 --> 00:23:25,840
I do not agree to this.

293
00:23:31,970 --> 00:23:34,300
Book of One's Crimes?

294
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:37,840
The one who wants the Longevity fruit the most is Fu Lou.

295
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:41,280
He would do this without a second thought even if he thinks it is fake

296
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:44,170
but this is a trap.

297
00:23:44,970 --> 00:23:48,220
Miss Chun Hua, how can you be so sure that

298
00:23:48,220 --> 00:23:51,520
Fu Lou would fall for this without a second of doubt?

299
00:23:53,970 --> 00:23:57,350
The most precious thing to Fu Lou is his wife.

300
00:23:57,350 --> 00:24:01,810
His wife is currently very ill and needs this Longevity fruit the most,

301
00:24:01,810 --> 00:24:04,870
but this Longevity fruit is fake.

302
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:10,140
Miss Chun Hua,

303
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:13,790
I once heard you say this before.

304
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:20,230
That's true! According to the rumors, Fu Lou's wife, You Si, is gravely ill.

305
00:24:20,230 --> 00:24:23,120
Fu Lou has been worried over this.

306
00:24:23,950 --> 00:24:27,960
This rumor coincidently matches with the existence of the Book of One's Crimes.

307
00:24:29,100 --> 00:24:32,440
Could it be too good to be true?

308
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:41,920
I'm afraid his feelings... can't be compared to the absolute sincerity for Miss Leng.

309
00:25:33,540 --> 00:25:37,090
Were you happy to return to Fengming Mountain Manor?

310
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:43,180
Is it because of Xiao Bai that you don't act flirtatiously with your brother?

311
00:25:47,140 --> 00:25:50,100
Based on your reaction, does that mean you admit to it?

312
00:25:58,420 --> 00:26:02,830
- Older Brother! 
 - I thought you never wanted to see me again, based on our last encounter.

313
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:07,230
Today, I passed by coincidently and found out that you were looking for the ice silkworm pearl.

314
00:26:08,090 --> 00:26:11,610
- Older Brother, I was just really desperate! 
 - Look!

315
00:26:11,610 --> 00:26:14,780
The one you think of when you're desperate is also your older brother.

316
00:26:28,740 --> 00:26:33,270
If you return it to me again, you will never see me again.

317
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:41,500
Older Brother, can you take me to Chuanqi Gorge?

318
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:50,230
The Cave Master of Qianyue Sect committed so many crimes.

319
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:52,240
He never does anything out of goodwill.

320
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:54,810
But since it is your request,

321
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:58,180
then I must fulfill your request.

322
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:16,140
Do you really like Lady Fu?

323
00:27:17,270 --> 00:27:18,880
She is a very nice lady.

324
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:21,710
No wonder you wanted me to ask her for help last time.

325
00:27:25,260 --> 00:27:27,700
What good is it to have a weak heart?

326
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:30,420
Fu Lou was ultimately brought down by her.

327
00:27:30,420 --> 00:27:32,710
If it was not for her,

328
00:27:32,710 --> 00:27:35,700
Qianyua Sect, Chuanqi Sect, and Fengming Mountain Manor;

329
00:27:35,700 --> 00:27:39,650
the situation of the three pillars wouldn't have persisted until now.

330
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:45,000
I've met Fu Lou.

331
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:47,900
Although he acted decisively and cruelly,

332
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:51,800
he definitely is not a brute nor an unconscionable person.

333
00:27:52,550 --> 00:27:55,950
If he could find a woman to stay by his side at an earlier time,

334
00:27:55,950 --> 00:27:59,690
he wouldn't be in this chaotic martial art world now.

335
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:03,630
However, he has found Madame You Si

336
00:28:04,230 --> 00:28:07,460
who is soft-hearted and kind.

337
00:28:08,070 --> 00:28:10,410
She is even in such a fragile health.

338
00:28:12,220 --> 00:28:15,180
Fu Lou knows it,

339
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:18,480
that's why he doesn't let her go out of the valley to be seen easily.

340
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:23,580
However, Xiao Chun Hua is very special.

341
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:27,090
You were the first to notice Fu Lou's weakness.

342
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:33,730
Perhaps...

343
00:28:34,620 --> 00:28:37,090
This is what made me give up immortality

344
00:28:37,090 --> 00:28:39,490
and this is the love that I also want to find.

345
00:28:48,380 --> 00:28:51,610
Don't hurt Fu Lou and Madam You Si.

346
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:56,580
If I wanted to do that, they wouldn't still be alive now.

347
00:28:57,230 --> 00:28:59,870
You don't want to kill Fu Lou?

348
00:28:59,870 --> 00:29:01,910
I don't want to.

349
00:29:01,910 --> 00:29:05,040
Fu Lou must not die by my hands.

350
00:29:06,660 --> 00:29:08,680
You are so right.

351
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:11,640
After all, Chuanqi Gorge is not that easy to deal with.

352
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:15,670
If you kill him, wouldn't you have another group of enemies?

353
00:29:17,130 --> 00:29:19,830
I'm never afraid of too many enemies.

354
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:22,820
Besides, it is not that difficult to kill Fu Lou.

355
00:29:24,780 --> 00:29:30,280
Older Brother, comparing you with Fu Lou, whose martial arts is better?

356
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:35,280
Xiao Chun Hua, you don't need martial arts to kill Fu Lou.

357
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:38,940
The key is to know a person's weakness.

358
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:41,020
If you know his weakness,

359
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:44,480
he will be much easier to deal with.

360
00:29:49,930 --> 00:29:53,490
Right! You have no weakness.

361
00:29:56,190 --> 00:29:58,340
Older Brother has a weakness.

362
00:29:58,340 --> 00:30:00,710
My weakness is you.

363
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:04,500
Be careful in the future!

364
00:30:21,560 --> 00:30:24,380
This Yousi is easy to deal with,

365
00:30:24,380 --> 00:30:27,650
