369
00:30:41,090 --> 00:30:43,430
Making fun of others must be amusing?

370
00:30:44,340 --> 00:30:49,370
I see Master Fu Lou is concerned about the chaos.

371
00:30:49,370 --> 00:30:53,040
So you came to Chuanqi Gorge to make fun of me?

372
00:30:53,040 --> 00:30:54,800
That is where you are wrong.

373
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:59,040
This time, I came here to help Master Fu Lou.

374
00:30:59,880 --> 00:31:03,090
I've asked you to join forces before.

375
00:31:03,090 --> 00:31:05,570
At that time, you flatly refused.

376
00:31:07,110 --> 00:31:10,290
I don't believe that you can be so kind now.

377
00:31:10,290 --> 00:31:13,200
I indeed don't have much kindness.

378
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:15,500
However, for my younger sister,

379
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:18,640
