380
00:31:23,730 --> 00:31:25,520
Your internal strength.

381
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:28,460
I already said it, Master Fu Lou.

382
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:32,490
It's more troublesome to make me to be an opponent than a helper.

383
00:31:32,490 --> 00:31:36,340
The helper you mean... is her right?

384
00:31:40,650 --> 00:31:42,590
It's me!

385
00:31:44,230 --> 00:31:48,650
Since she hasn't the Longevity fruit, she is useless.

386
00:31:48,650 --> 00:31:51,900
My younger sister is quite useful.

387
00:31:52,690 --> 00:31:58,270
Gorge Master Fu, Fengming Mountain Manor is about to hold a Longevity fruit conference in these two days.

